summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the creation of a Seattle-King County Taxicab Commission to advise and make recommendations to the City of Seattle and King County Councils, establishing a new Chapter to the Seattle Municipal Code, and repealing Chapter 3.63 of the Seattle Municipal Code.
